eval/runs.sqlite-*
# `eval/baselines/` is intentionally tracked — committed numbers are
# the regression artifact for layer-1 (and later) eval runs (see
# PLAN task 2.7 / decision D-68). Per-pair `*_report.json` dumps are
# the raw `ScorePairResult` per case and exceed the pre-commit
# large-file limit; they're reproducible from `eval/runs.sqlite` and
# the diagnostics/summary JSONs alongside them carry the actual
# regression-relevant numbers.
eval/baselines/**/*_report.json

